'''Futor's Network''' was an information network company founded by the [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustan]] [[Futor]] on ''[[Omze's Incredible Traveling Starport/Legends|Omze's Incredible Traveling Starport]]''. It was located next to [[Con'varra's Datawork Central]]. The office contained a couch for customers to sit on while Futor looked up the data they had requested. It also had a counter and work table covered in [[Datapad/Legends|datapads]]. Futor's Network would provide information and access to newsnets and other services to the patrons of the Starport.

